### 1. Create Goal for Employee
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/goals
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "title": "Improve Code Quality",
  "description": "Increase test coverage to 80%",
  "weightage": 30.00,
  "period": "2026-Q1",
  "assignedToId": 2
}

### 2. Create Second Goal
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/goals
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "title": "Deliver Features on Time",
  "description": "Complete all sprint tasks",
  "weightage": 40.00,
  "period": "2026-Q1",
  "assignedToId": 2
}

### 3. Create Third Goal
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/goals
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "title": "Customer Satisfaction",
  "description": "Maintain high customer ratings",
