### 4. Create Goal weightage exceeded (422)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/goals
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "title": "Extra Goal",
  "description": "This should fail",
  "weightage": 10.00,
  "period": "2026-Q1",
  "assignedToId": 2
}

### 5. Get Goal by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/goals/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 6. Get Goal not found (404)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/goals/999
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 7. Get Goals by User
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/goals/user/2
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 8. Update Goal
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/goals/1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "title": "Improve Code Quality Updated",
  "description": "Increase test coverage to 90%",
  "weightage": 30.00,
  "period": "2026-Q1",
  "assignedToId": 2
}

### 9. Delete Goal
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/goals/3
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}